channel.title: Final PvP release
channel.description:
Yo wassup, i've decided to release this, as i'm most likly going back to making a PvP server, not an eco based server. This server was up for about 1week, and it got around 25-30 players, who all enjoyed it alot.this,
I hope you have alot off fun with this one, as much as i did <3 This server, is a PI Base (project insanity.)
